data.name: MessageBox_DeepCleanWarning
data.value:
!! WARNING !! WARNING !! WARNING !!
You are about to perform a DEEP CLEAN of your NMT. All default applications will be reinstalled, all customizations removed. After reboot you will be offered to do a TYPICAL or FRESH setup. A typical setup will keep your Media files while a fresh setup will do a complete wipe of your HDD.
A DEEP CLEAN WILL REMOVE ANY NON-DEFAULT FOLDERS AND ALL SETTINGS FILES FROM YOU NMT.
ALL FOLDERS AND FILES WILL BE REMOVED, EXCEPT THE FOLLOWING FOLDERS: Download, Music, Photo, Podcast, Video In effect all files and folders except the default media folders will be removed! A backup of these folders and files will be made in new folder called CleanBackup.
Using this option IS COMPLETELY AT OWN RISK! Are you sure you want to continue?
